e5d607","tid":1153473,"uid":18955,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"quote":{"pid":"0031329968a9747aa866486d9b731b09044360b3","tid":1153473,"uid":48011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T22:37:57.000Z","msg":"誠哥走佬都仲唔信 抵你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T22:44:13.000Z","msg":"諗起誠哥馬雲馬化騰比賽跑步個笑話<br />\n<br />\n「中國先先後後的首富們，包括王健林、馬雲、馬化騰、劉強東和許家印，約香港的李嘉誠一起賽跑。中國的首富們都嘲笑李嘉誠年紀大，腿腳不利索，笑他肯定跑不快，結果最後卻是李嘉誠跑了第一。大家都在奇怪為啥他能得第一，李嘉誠大笑說，誰叫你們聽到槍聲才跑的！」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:05:27.000Z","msg":"其他首富想跑但係已經冇機會跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578d844f395d0fed139ee4ddb086dba17f5e4d48","tid":1153473,"uid":245441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:09:32.000Z","msg":"所謂既一帶一路其實係將對中國既投資轉向其他一帶一路既國家"},{"pid":"b930ce4525913a5b10d9c6f8a59e102a3f2bcee5","tid":1153473,"uid":16970,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:12:18.000Z","msg":"1/4生意受影響 劉達邦：生產線或遷東南亞<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文章日期：2018年9月20日</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】颱風「山竹」雖已過，但港商隨即迎來另一場「十級風暴」，美國前日宣布下周一（24日）以2000億美元貨值關稅「賀中秋」，涉及產品更廣泛，受影響港商亦更多。其中，香港中小型企業聯合會永遠榮譽主席、香港金邊實業董事總經理<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">劉達邦</span></strong>（圖）亦無法倖免，出口美國的300萬美元產品也在今次清單之上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉達邦表示，美國佔公司四分之一生意額，大約為300萬美元左右，「從年初已經與美國客戶保持聯繫，開頭未殺到埋身，對方沒什麼表示」，但之後當貿易戰不斷升溫，對方也曾透露不排除在東南亞另找供應商。<br />\n<br />\n客戶訂單至明年5月<br />\n<br />\n劉達邦稱，與該客戶的訂單去到明年5月，目前完成四分之一貨量，因此餘下四分之三無可避免要徵10%關稅。「幸好我們的合約是先付30%訂金，貨物出港再收35%，餘下35%收貨支付，所以就算對方拒絕收貨也未至於全賠」，但他也指出，知道有些港商會給客戶數期，這樣的話，被拖數甚至臨時取消訂單的風險便更大。<br />\n<br />\n劉達邦坦言，美國業務原本逐步增長，前景明朗，現在爆發貿易戰令情况逆轉，對公司影響深遠，連他也不禁萌生過去30年都從沒考慮過的搬廠念頭，可能要將生產線遷至東南亞或不受關稅影響地區，「目前要看客戶還肯不肯落新單」。<br />\n<br />\n人幣貶值 有空間減價「走盞」<br />\n<br />\n他表示，下個月會赴美國與該客戶傾談，唯一慶幸的是這段時間人民幣貶值，令公司有一些減價空間，就算對方提出要分擔部分稅負也能「走盞」，然而如果明年1月1日之前中美之間關係沒好轉餘地，關稅稅率按既定安排由10%上調至25%，「到時真係唔知可以點」。<br />\n<br />\n====<br />\n<br />\n九月果陣諗到而家都唔搬就抵你瀨嘢啦."},{"pid":"d597f787fc0b9f4285f37198dd66f0dd8936d216","tid":1153473,"uid":164980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0837f77cf8a73828fdad7cb212ae5b2c2bd5d49f","tid":1153473,"uid":230146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52cd517bc5a30ddd5dddf8c71a7447038a61c10b","tid":1153473,"uid":4964,"like":383,"dislike":7,"score":376,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他後悔錯判了貿易戰形式，沒有早一點撤資。</span><br />\n<br />\n做左幾十年人,對政治形勢判斷仲衰過連登仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:28:12.000Z","msg":"我討厭政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859b2b3cb2b13169c17bb92e95c3404e1a2fa91c","tid":1153473,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fff2a31c0d75d5d431c18f61049e720fece20b2e","tid":1153473,"uid":1372,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"52cd517bc5a30ddd5dddf8c71a7447038a61c10b","tid":1153473,"uid":4964,"like":383,"dislike":7,"score":376,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他後悔錯判了貿易戰形式，沒有早一點撤資。</span><br />\n<br />\n做左幾十年人,對政治形勢判斷仲衰過連登仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"果一代人唔使有腦都可以發達架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:28:32.000Z","msg":"有咁易發達個個人老豆做左富豪啦 有撚人住公屋咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29155777e9f50d36b2fe9b71f9d6082c208f8fe","tid":1153473,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"859b2b3cb2b13169c17bb92e95c3404e1a2fa91c","tid":1153473,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fff2a31c0d75d5d431c18f61049e720fece20b2e","tid":1153473,"uid":1372,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"52cd517bc5a30ddd5dddf8c71a7447038a61c10b","tid":1153473,"uid":4964,"like":383,"dislike":7,"score":376,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他後悔錯判了貿易戰形式，沒有早一點撤資。</span><br />\n<br />\n做左幾十年人,對政治形勢判斷仲衰過連登仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"果一代人唔使有腦都可以發達架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:28:32.000Z","msg":"有咁易發達個個人老豆做左富豪啦 有撚人住公屋咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班下層慘喇 上面做錯決定又要炒佢地"},{"pid":"88fa8f71e72fef59941ea74ccba02a5f48f04587","tid":1153473,"uid":192327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:33:37.000Z","msg":"香港就係衰係哩d人手上"},{"pid":"c82b4420f669624212fba788b34f7359adfd4be8","tid":1153473,"uid":89834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:39:36.000Z","msg":"過左引渡條例一定捉撚晒呢班含家剷出黎槍斃"},{"pid":"629cf534adbf105df636ae2a9268886d29f53be6","tid":1153473,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:43:28.000Z","msg":"等睇走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6536cc4d4638359370e27f8c45cf65608947010","tid":1153473,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"625883d45e5d9c4cab440e6389f80945c937f30b","tid":1153473,"uid":42340,"like":26,"dislike":50,"score":-24,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"我同意香港會仆街<br />\n股價會跌<br />\n<br />\n但樓價一定唔會<br />\n因為係剛需"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:45:22.000Z","msg":"經濟可以分開後計？<br />\n先股後樓市<br />\n次次都係"},{"pid":"3e2b0353919f341831ca6e6e5fe986b605e7e863","tid":1153473,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:49:30.000Z","msg":"想走？無咁容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0116685faeefcfefc69b9d7f1ff57c5fa32726e1","tid":1153473,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"誠哥又贏"},{"pid":"6aac9e0eb63a4635f2ce5d9222d1b1b957cf4845","tid":1153473,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:52:52.000Z","msg":"柒婆:美中貿易戰對香港影響輕微<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dc8d63bb525d186f764c4545318f4605143d47","tid":1153473,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:54:13.000Z","msg":"咁唔愛國？沒收佢本passport !!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b82d5f4928612e721e05643c6c37fbb8feb3e7","tid":1153473,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2688a6cd6a0f434d9562662f5c3fe30ef7e436","tid":1153473,"uid":196965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:59:24.000Z","msg":"教授叫人沽港元買美金<br />\n香港有聯繫匯率咁做有咩意思<br />\n同金管局做對沖？"},{"pid":"aa16c9dc508b454738eb75b45df70e0d1f682e92","tid":1153473,"uid":69563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db2688a6cd6a0f434d9562662f5c3fe30ef7e436","tid":1153473,"uid":196965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:59:24.000Z","msg":"教授叫人沽港元買美金<br />\n香港有聯繫匯率咁做有咩意思<br />\n同金管局做對沖？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:04:18.000Z","msg":"買美女做定期，息口高過港女。"},{"pid":"517bcf59b8b3c837abe05a5b38624f7d2d9513b3","tid":1153473,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:07:33.000Z","msg":"轉貼<br />\n<br />\n其實這波貿易戰，中國很明顯的是在安撫內憂，川普是在挑起匯率戰，<br />\n<br />\n產業最重要的有二個，一個是市場，第二是供應鍊。<br />\n<br />\n一、市場美國為中高端消費的主要市場不予質疑，但川普在意的是中國以集中資源補助國企快速成長，並滲入他國事務，這有違川普的白人優越主義，加上中國內需市場的成長停滯，美企無法賺到更多的利潤，是時候讓大國夢停止。<br />\n<br />\n二、會到中國設廠的二種廠商，一個是看中低廉的人事土地成本，因為中國政府為吸引外資投產，給予土地及稅賦優惠，但崛起後陸續收回，生產成本不再低廉時，就會引發第二種設廠的廠商，供應鍊的齊全度，但一個產業鍊上下游紛紛外移到東南亞時，雖有東協國家的優惠，但還是擋不住向外擴場的動力。<br />\n<br />\n三、回到這次的貿易戰，中國現在想安撫內憂，提出關稅的主要承接者為美國消費者，這樣講以國際貿易角度完全正確，但中國生產並不是寡佔，而是開放市場，關稅變成25%，拆盤到RSP一定高於25%，消費者有權力選擇非中國製商品，而選擇阿墨代工或東南亞代工製造的商品，以取得較低的購入成本，這時中國的代工產業鍊撐外移的更嚴重，甚至數十倍都有可能，因為東協國家的免關稅優勢，可能有部份產業改設東南亞，以免關稅方式銷售中國，只剩銷售部隊在中國，產業全部外移。<br />\n<br />\n四、一間公司的產品，我通常定位成營收創造者但低毛利，另一種是毛利創造者但低營收但當你少了大量的代工低毛利案子，就算想靠剩下的內銷，也可能使基本營收下降許多，當下降了，很多人事固定費用是從這裏去攤提的，利潤不是同比例下降，而且超越比例的下降，裁員縮減產線是必然的，但裁員了就更沒有內需市場消費力，每況愈下。<br />\n<br />\n五、當內需市場景氣低迷(現在就超低迷了)，政府為了表面數字好看，就更多的大型建設投入，別忘了，中國的成長率是建構在大型建設以及房地產投資下，但利率是一個很大的問題，市場低迷，大家繳不出房貸，銀行呆帳是天文數字，勢必需降息救市，或印製更多的鈔票，但印鈔票是通膨的開始，房市崩盤沒地方住就會暴動，利率波動相對影響股市及匯市，如果有天美金兌人民幣是一比八也不意外了。<br />\n<br />\n六、這時一代一路的國家發現中國無法再提供鉅額投資，或不像計劃中的美夢，中國就會變成新一代的鎖國，因為越南、柬埔寨、緬甸、印度等國因代工而興起，人口紅利不再，少子化的後果使得人口也漸漸老化，年輕一代的經濟更沉重，這是一個很可怕且可能發生的未來。"},{"pid":"ff56ad1abf61a932aeede69c3838318d5c202150","tid":1153473,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:09:32.000Z","msg":"簡單講，絕大部分廠都係美國單用黎頂燈油火蠟，其他單搵錢。<br />\n<br />\n冇左美國單，單靠其他單係頂唔住個固定開支。"},{"pid":"e4a5bbb8e304b5074f4c09fa625925dcfa6bfe9c","tid":1153473,"uid":160747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"625883d45e5d9c4cab440e6389f80945c937f30b","tid":1153473,"uid":42340,"like":26,"dislike":50,"score":-24,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"我同意香港會仆街<br />\n股價會跌<br />\n<br />\n但樓價一定唔會<br />\n因為係剛需"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:29:46.000Z","msg":"樓價一定會跌如果股價跌，因為買樓會難左<br />\n銀行睇到個市咁差一定調高壓力測試<br />\n<br />\n少人買到，業主又想出貨套現撈股市底，所以一定會跌不過都未必買到"},{"pid":"8eb86f5808d9ec26b81e0f5dbd29ca5a613811dd","tid":1153473,"uid":108814,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52cd517bc5a30ddd5dddf8c71a7447038a61c10b","tid":1153473,"uid":4964,"like":383,"dislike":7,"score":376,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他後悔錯判了貿易戰形式，沒有早一點撤資。</span><br />\n<br />\n做左幾十年人,對政治形勢判斷仲衰過連登仔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:34:59.000Z","msg":"連登仔咪成日支爆 爆左十年 最叻馬後炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f168f6b0f853679f41b081a27e18e61d476e288e","tid":1153473,"uid":142025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccb082c65f806df40c64d159a67f59f9f2e5d607","tid":1153473,"uid":18955,"like":77,